          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἀορτήρ, ῆρος</span></b>  (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἀείρω</span>): <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">baldric, belt</span>, usually
          for the <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἄορ</span>, and the same as <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">τελαμών</span> (see cut), <i><span class="en">Od. 11.609</span></i>; ‘strap’ for a wallet, <i><span class="en">Od. 13.438</span></i>; what the ‘suspenders’ were in <i><span class="en">Il. 11.31</span></i> is not perfectly
          clear.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
